
                            About application
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. General information
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  This software is an electrontube circuit sizing application.
  There are these calculations:

  - AC coupled cathode follower with triode
  - Cathodyne phase inverter #1
  - Cathodyne phase inverter #2
  - Current stabilised heating circuit with baretter (Fe-H resistor)
  - Grounded cathode amplifier with triode
  - Grounded cathode amplifier with triode (with bypassed cathode resistor)
  - Grounded cathode amplifier with triode cascode #1
  - Grounded cathode amplifier with triode cascode #2
  - Grounded cathode amplifier with triode with negative feedback
  - Mu-follower amplifier with triodes
  - Shunt regulated push-pull (SRPP) amplifier with triodes
  - Voltage regulator with gas filled voltage stabiliser tube

  This is a software, which does not cost money (maybe you must pay for use
Internet).  The lope conditions is the acceptance and observance of the European
Union Public Licence.
   
   OS support: FreeBSD, Linux and Windows.
   Language support: English and Hungarian.

2. Installer packages
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. for FreeBSD
   electrontubes-0.4.1-FreeBSD-Port.shar   port package
   electrontubes-0.4.1.txz                 binary package

b. for Linux
   electrontubes-0.4.1-1.i586.rpm          binary package
   electrontubes-0.4.1-i586-1.txz          binary package
   electrontubes-0.4.1-i586.bin            installer programme
   electrontubes-0.4.1-i586.tar.gz         binary package
   electrontubes-0.4.1.x86.package         binary package
   electrontubes_0.4.1-1_i386.deb          binary package

c. for Windows
   electrontubes-0.4.1-win32.exe           installer application
   electrontubes-0.4.1-win32.msi           binary package
   electrontubes-0.4.1-win32.zip           binary package

d. source code
   electrontubes-0.4.1.tar.gz              source package

3. Settings
~~~~~~~~~~~
  On Linux and FreeBSD use 'LANG' environment variable to set language of the
application. (English: en_US, Hungarian: hu_HU)

